Package: tidycops
Type: Package
Title: Standardized R Access to Public Police Incident Data
Version: 0.2.0
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Authors@R: person("Anthony", "Galvan", , "anthony.m.galvan@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Anthony Galvan [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Anthony Galvan <anthony.m.galvan@gmail.com>
Description: Provides a city-agnostic API wrapper to download, normalize,
    and query public police incident datasets. Includes a standardized incident
    schema, source crosswalks for multiple cities, and Dallas-focused legacy
    helpers retained for compatibility.
